            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.321,
                0.458,
                0.4
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "目的：从 \\(p(x)\\) 中抽取样本"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.487,
                0.797,
                0.563
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法：从 \\(g(x)\\) 中抽取样本，并按一定的概率接收"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.652,
                0.595,
                0.73
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "要求: 存在 \\(M\\), 使得 \\(p(x) \\leq M g(x)\\)"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.144,
                0.197,
                0.235
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "步骤"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.321,
                0.568,
                0.4
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "1. 从 \\(g(x)\\) 中抽取样本, 并记为 \\(x^{*}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.505,
                0.656,
                0.626
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "2. 计算 \\(r = \\frac{p\\left(x^{*}\\right)}{M g\\left(x^{*}\\right)}\\), 并从 \\(U[0,1]\\) 中抽取 \\(u\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.082,
                0.698,
                0.906,
                0.909
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "3. 若 \\(u \\leq r\\), 则令 \\(x = x^{*}\\) 即为从 \\(p(x)\\) 中抽取的样本; 否则重复1.和2."
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "bbox": [
