            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} F (t) = P (x \\leq t) = \\frac {P (x ^ {*} \\leq t , u \\leq r)}{P (u \\leq r)} = \\frac {\\frac {1}{M} \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {t} p (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*}}{\\frac {1}{M}} \\\\ = \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {t} p (x ^ {*}) d x ^ {*} \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
